snippet.title: Filmmaker Rob Reiner Has Serious Words For Donald Trump | Morning Joe | MSNBC

localized.description:
Filmmaker Rob Reiner joins Morning Joe to discuss his thoughts on Donald Trump, who he says is only taken seriously as a political candidate because Trump is a celebrity.
